<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你待會<delay8 />要參加釣魚大會對吧？<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「和我一決勝負吧！」<delay frames="40" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />……雖然我想這麼說啦，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但釣魚大會<delay8 />並不是對戰形式的大會。<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay20 />氣勢上我是絕對不會輸的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說釣魚大會是<delay8 />只要釣到越多魚，<delay8 />
就能拿到越多點數來著？<pageBreak />簡單地說，<delay20 /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是不管什麼魚都行，<delay8 />
只要看到就拼命釣，對吧？<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是簡單明瞭！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說到魚啊，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />生活在池塘或沼澤中的魚<delay8 />
因為會有腥味，所以不太討喜啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />要是能活用這點來烹調的話，<delay20 />
應該有方法讓這種魚<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />發揮牠獨有的特色吧！<10_4 />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真讓人想<delay8 />努力開發食譜呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />釣魚大會的氣氛<delay8 />好像非常熱烈呢！<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不參加嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想參加的人<delay20 />只要到廣場上
跟<colour id="3" />俞司廷<colour id="65535" />說一聲就行了吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你問我「怎麼不參加釣魚大會」？<delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為我總覺得<delay8 />今天沒心情釣魚呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在興致來的時候<delay8 />做喜歡做的事，<delay8 />
這可是我的信念！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過也對，<delay8 />我既喜歡魚，<delay8 />
而且也不討厭釣魚嘛。<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我下次會參加的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>